    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elementris is like Tetris, but the element of color finally got a meaning</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tiles of the same color don't go together</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place up to 20 different shapes of 4 different colors on the grid without a gap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shapes can be anything from dominoes to pentominoes, depending on your skill</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amend your mistakes with helpful power-ups like the Eraser, the Hammer and the Colorizer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your skills in 2 different game modes as the game gets faster and faster</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the direction of gravity</p></li></ul>",
